text:
EFL gun to the dogs Neil Ashton: Arsene Wenger has to leave Arsenal and it’s time to start building a team to finally win trophies 
Our man on the sorry state of affairs at the Emirates in a humiliating time... and who could replace the Frenchman at the helm Comment By Neil ashton, chief football writer 16th February 2017, 11:01 pm
